The '''Bothan Spynet'''<ref name="Rebel Files">''[[Star Wars: The Rebel Files]]''</ref> was a well-organized intelligence network that was active during the time of the [[Galactic Civil War]]. A [[Kupohan]] named [[Sakhet]] occasionally did contract work for the [[Bothan]] spynet, running a small [[Sakhet's Noodles|noodle hut]] as a front of her intelligence services.<ref name="HTTJ" /> The [[Bothan|members]] of the spynet [[Bothan Spynet intelligence operation|found out]] about the [[Endor|location]] of the [[DS-2 Death Star II Mobile Battle Station|Second Death Star]] for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|Rebel Alliance]] to prepare their [[Battle of Endor|assault]] on the Death Star II, despite suffering heavy casualties.<ref name="ROTJ" />

